This item commemorates the 2015 DreamHack Cluj-Napoca CS:GO Championship.
It was dropped during the Group Stage match between mousesports and G2 Esports, and autographed by Fatih Dayik who was the most valuable player in that round.

More accurate but less damaging than its AK-47 counterpart, the M4A4 is the full-auto assault rifle of choice for CTs. It has individual parts spray-painted solid colors in a tornado color scheme. Don't be fooled by its simplicity
The Inferno Collection
Sticker: G2 Esports (Gold) | Cluj-Napoca 2015, DreamHack (Gold) | Cluj-Napoca 2015, mousesports (Gold) | Cluj-Napoca 2015, gob b (Gold) | Cluj-Napoca 2015
Exterior: Factory New

Powerful and reliable, the AK-47 is one of the most popular assault rifles in the world. It is most deadly in short, controlled bursts of fire. It has been custom painted with a deer and dreamcatchers in neon colors and finished with a pearlescent effect. I've been saving this for a special occasion... – Booth, Arms Dealer
The Dreams & Nightmares Collection
Exterior: Factory New
A low-recoil firearm with a high rate of fire, the P250 is a relatively inexpensive choice against armored opponents. It is spray-painted all white. It looks pure, but looks can be deceiving
